This is the Doom variant

Place on map and use the first two arguments to control the intensity and area of the 
spawner. 

Second argument controls the size of the area. 32 for example, spawns in a 64x64x64 qube.

Third argument controls the chance of sparkles being spawned. 255 spawns no sparkles at all.

It should be noted that pngs can't be translated like normal graphics. Because of this, if
you convert the SKFXA0 sprite to a png, the spawners will spawn white effects. Use Doom's
lmp format, instead.
